::Koj::
Starting to move faster "Someones watching us there in this area!"
Scanning with a sweep.

::?1::
"Ready?" As he takes off with extreme speed drawing the Crystal edged sword 
and jumps.

::Koj::
Snaps to gather the lances and jumps.

::Both::
Take one good swing landing on opposite sides.

::?1::
Has a nice gash on his shoulder.

::Koj::
"You have gotten soft on me" Laughing when a cut appears under his eye.

::?1::
"You don't get soft fighting a war." Laughing "Well met Koj"

::Koj::
"The Burning Noble and still fire hearted"

::?1::
"Don't call me that I hate that name.Whats going on."

::Koj explains all::
